Output docs/demo-login.gif

Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Width 1920
Set Height 1080
Set FontSize 24
Set Framerate 60
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Padding 20
Set PlaybackSpeed 1

Sleep 500ms
Type "zlib login"
Enter
Sleep 1s

# Fill email field
Type "user@example.com"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 500ms

# Fill password field
Type "mypassword123"
Enter
Sleep 5s
